&lt;p&gt;Join our team to take ownership of our MuleSoft platform and drive our integration strategy forward. As a MuleSoft Integration Engineer, you will design, develop, and maintain secure, scalable APIs, Mule applications and integration flows using the Anypoint Platform. You will play a critical role in centralizing our integrations across Fuze Health to deliver a unified API-led architecture that supports our growth and AI readiness.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
