&lt;li&gt;Testing: Develop maintainable test automation and ensure high code coverage for all integration artifacts.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Requirements&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience: Minimum 3–5 years of hands-on experience with MuleSoft Anypoint Platform (Mule 4, Anypoint Studio, CloudHub 2.0).&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
